It has a lovely atmosphere, it is small, personal, the staff are very friendly and it felt like a home from home.	This is a small, refined European style hotel with a quiet, reserved atmosphere decorated in muted colors and historical prints.	We had dinner at the hotel, our waiter was attentive and the dinner was very good, but nothing about it was truly memorable.	When it comes to service, value, atmosphere, professional/friendly staff, large, well equipped rooms, you will not find a better hotel.	We spent many an hour enjoying cocktails in the bar in the evening - it had a wonderful atmosphere.